Foresight User Guide

Run
===
To run it, execute:
  $ ./foresight-user-guide

Hacking
=======
* Written in mallard [0].

* All content is under the 'help' directory.

* The 'guide' directory contains the old user guide written in docbook. Please
  don't bother to update stuff there.

* See the TODO file for what to do.

Links
====
0. http://projectmallard.org/
